    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im having some really sharp pain in my stomach. it started around my belly button earlier today but now it's moved down to the lower right side. i think it might just be bad gas or maybe really bad period cramps? i really need to get some sleep though, can i just take some extra strength ibuprofen or maybe some oxy if i have it to sleep it off? it's just really uncomfortable",
