      "content": "wait really? appendicitis sounds so extreme. i barely even have a fever and i can still move around okay. i'm just really stressed about the cost of the ER and the wait times too. if i just take a high dose of tylenol it'll probably just calm my stomach down, right? it's more likely i just ate something weird than having emergency surgery.",
